data.description: Welcome to this impeccable home that exquisitely showcases upgrades and offers a touch of architectural elegance. Step inside and be greeted by an impressive 11-foot Raised Vaulted Ceiling that adds grandeur to the space. The stone-designed front elevation sets the tone for what lies within.    This stunning Estate features an inviting open floor plan, comprising 3 spacious bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms. The master suite offers a private oasis, and the beautifully appointed bathrooms provide both comfort and style.    Outside, the covered lanai beckons you to unwind while enjoying the serene views of the conservation area. It’s the perfect spot for morning coffee or evening relaxation.    As a resident, you’ll have access to the exceptional Amenity Center, complete with a meticulously designed fitness center for your active lifestyle, an inviting pool for those sunny Florida days, and an engaging playground for family fun, among other amenities.    This is more than a house; it’s your new home – a true haven of comfort and elegance. Don’t miss the opportunity to make it yours. Schedule a viewing today and experience the lifestyle this property has to offer!
